Key Insights & Findings

Target Audience: Women are the primary buyers, contributing to approximately 64% of total sales.
Age Demographics: The Adult age group (30-49 years) is the highest contributing segment (~50%).
Top Channels: Amazon, Myntra, and Flipkart are the leading sales channels, with Amazon alone accounting for ~35% of total orders.
Regional Dominance: Maharashtra, Karnataka, and Uttar Pradesh are the top 3 states, making up a significant portion of the revenue.
Peak Month: March recorded the highest sales and order volume during the year.
Order Fulfillment: More than 90% of orders were successfully delivered.

üõ†Ô∏è Tools & Technologies Used
Microsoft Excel: Used for data cleaning, processing, and creating pivot tables.
Data Visualization: Interactive dashboards and charts (Bar charts, Pie charts, and Line graphs) were used to represent the trends.
Data Cleaning: Handled missing values, standardized categories (e.g., consistent naming for Gender and Size), and created new columns like "Age Group".

üìÅ Dataset Description
The dataset includes over 31,000 rows of transactional data with the following attributes:
Order ID & Cust ID: Unique identifiers for transactions and customers.
Gender & Age Group: Demographic information.
Channel: Sales platform (Amazon, Ajio, Myntra, etc.).
Category & Size: Product details (Kurta, Set, Western Dress, etc.).
Amount: Transaction value.
Location: City and State of the customer.
Status: Order status (Delivered, Cancelled, Returned, Refunded).

üöÄ Final Conclusion
To improve sales in 2023, Vrinda Store should focus on:
Targeting Women aged 30-49 through personalized marketing.
Running promotional campaigns on Amazon and Myntra.
Expanding inventory or localized ads in Maharashtra and Karnataka.
